metadata.name: A Field of Dreams #1/21
metadata.description:
A Field of Dreams, a piece that represents happiness and that dreams can come true!

Happiness and colourful days, something I hope I can spread with this edition (and my other work of course).

I have been very fortunate to be able to capture these beautiful foggy mornings. When I'm out photographing and all elements come together it always put a big smile upon my face. With this edition I hope I can do the same to you and this great community from which I have learned so much from. 

Why 21 pieces? Natural things follow the Fibonacci sequence. It appears in biological settings such as branching in trees etc. 21 is part of that sequence and because I love to photograph landscape & nature, 21 would be a good number to use!
